NO MORE FIRE raced six wide around the first turn, raced with the second flight early and lacked a bid. QUICKSTYLE prompt the pace from the outside of rivals and faded. LADY BOURBON broke in the air, void of early speed, shifted out to race from the far outside in the stretch and never threatened.
